item.title: CVE-2020-7838|2024-08-04T09:41:01.896Z -- smilegate -- stove%20client
item.description: A arbitrary code execution vulnerability exists in the way that the Stove client improperly validates input value. An attacker could execute arbitrary code when the user access to crafted web page. This issue affects: Smilegate STOVE Client 0.0.4.72.
